    "body": "In https://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/20817 , https://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/16684 we introduced `Q`:\r\n\r\n```\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t*Q*\r\nQ\t\t\tRepeat the last recorded register [count] times.\r\n\t\t\tSee |reg_recorded()|.\r\n```\r\n\r\nBut it doesn't work on a visual selection.\r\n\r\n## Expected behavior\r\n\r\n- `Q` on a visual selection should repeat the macro for each line. \r\n- similar for `@@` and `@{register}` ?\r\n\r\nBasically this mapping:\r\n\r\n    xnoremap Q :normal @<c-r>=reg_recorded()<cr><cr>\r\n\r\n",
